Package eu.h2020.helios_social.modules.socialgraphmining.heuristics

Class DifferenceMiner

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.h2020.helios_social.modules.socialgraphmining.SocialGraphMiner
      • eu.h2020.helios_social.modules.socialgraphmining.heuristics.DifferenceMiner
  • public class DifferenceMiner
extends SocialGraphMiner
    This class provides a SocialGraphMiner that wraps a miner predictions so as not to predict the top of a base miner's predictions (e.g. DHR@k,withhold of a miner is obtained if HitRate@k is calculated over the outcome of new AdditionalDiscoveryMiner(miner, new RepeatAndReplyMiner(cen), withhold).
    Author:
    Emmanouil Krasanakis
